Installing Phycas and the PhyPy library
=======================================

Windows
-------
Python 2.4 or 2.5 is a prerequisite
Run correct installer for your version of Python
If you have installed Python previously and have upgraded to 2.5, be sure your PATH 
  environmental variable includes the path to the python.exe file
After installing Phycas, you should find a Phycas folder in Start > All Programs...
  Choose the "Test Phycas" shortcut to run a series of tests (only takes a couple of minutes)

